html:
11.6.20  6:55 pm   If you could invent a word that meant many different things, what would it be?

      possibly set to music, because music is very useful for meaning enhancement

11.6.20  6:43 pm   you seem to get the same questions over and over, why don't you have an FAQ or something?

      as you've noticed, that's exactly what this is

11.6.20  6:24 pm   This is the infinity police. We've recieved many reports that you are trying to do infinity. Please stop or else you will be sad.

      so true

11.6.20  6:09 pm   do you like musical theater and if so what is your favorite musical 

      if possible i would prefer to make a new one to be my favorite

11.6.20  5:50 pm   when will you release a new song/video

      if i had my preference, extremely often. the main thing standing in the way of this is my pathological inability to stop being too complicated

11.6.20  5:17 pm   what is the most useful thing you know

      everyone might be each other

11.6.20  5:17 pm   I wanted to know what type of music I should try making, Since I do like your genre of music, but I don't feel like it would go very well with my guitar, and when I try to do stuff like you it doesn't come out very well, Should I Keep trying at it even though i'm not very proud of it or try something else?

      try anything you know. no matter what it is, you will probably have to adapt it somewhat for your instrumentational situation. perhaps especially with my music because i am often guilty of being very complicated, which i am not entirely proud of

11.6.20  5:05 pm   is grass edible?

      it might be

11.6.20  5:02 pm   Do you like jupiter

      yes

11.6.20  4:50 pm   opinions on goldfish

      is it a pet? is it a snack? check the packaging because there's 2 types

11.6.20  4:40 pm   What is your favourite video made by you

      i would prefer to make a new one to be my favorite

11.6.20  4:36 pm   what did you do at the airport terminal

      back in the good old days, i remember walking through the corridors and finding the correct plane which corresponded to my ticket, and maybe purchasing some name-brand meal items, at 2x price but with 2x nostalgia

11.6.20  4:35 pm   if a person who can see the future plays chess with another who can read minds, who wins?

      you have to watch and see, but how am i supposed to do that if you didn't even tell me when and where the game can be found

11.6.20  3:50 pm   In your video, "fish opinnions" You said that Sock should be 2 words.

     it's important to point out that that's a work of fiction

      Where would the space be, and would the same apply for "socks"?

     the reason 'sock' felt like a good choice for that line, is because the word sock seems to be extremely 1-syllable. very difficult and cumbersome to make sock into 2 syllables. let's just say i will leave that to the imagination

11.6.20  2:42 pm   Why is the rain so cool

      because it's so........ normal

11.6.20  2:37 pm   my music teacher is insane, will u be my music teacher?

      sure

11.6.20  2:19 pm   What is fun?

      movement, and motion

11.6.20  2:15 pm   what made you start to make videos

      too many thoughts and feelings. need some souvenirs, to prove they even happened

11.6.20  1:42 pm   I need some words of wisdom to help me through the day, can you provide some?

      yes

11.6.20  11:52 am   why is the earth flat?

      so it's easier to make maps

11.6.20  11:32 am   how to feel normal

      go through a door

11.6.20  11:08 am   i want to write music with bigger chords, and use more out there, jazzy and complex sounding chords with extensions and a rich color to it, but i never know how to use them, how would you use chords like that?

      wait until you actually need them to make the song good

11.6.20  10:42 am   Thoughts on the empire state building?

      you can find out what day it is just by looking at the color scheme

11.6.20  10:07 am   whats your favorite food

      trash

11.6.20  10:05 am   vowels or consonants? 

      one weird trick, which linguists HATE, is using them both together

11.6.20  9:55 am   If given the opportunity to score a film, would you take that opportunity?

      yes but, it would probably be me who gave myself the opportunity

11.6.20  8:40 am   If you could invent a new color, what would you name it?

      wait, first things first, what does it look like

11.6.20  7:56 am   What goes through your head?

      way too many things at the same time

11.6.20  6:50 am   When will you release another song?

      as soon as i can

11.6.20  5:52 am   What bad thing did you do that you made a song about it?

      none. the bad thing was making a song about having done a fictional bad thing

11.6.20  4:18 am   did you predict the future or did you make the future

      i make the future but it is an extremely collaborative effort with the entire rest of the universe including and most especially you

11.6.20  3:06 am   Are you creating a 3 hour special that is coming out in 2030?

      if so, i haven't started it yet. there will be many things that are a lot shorter, before then

11.6.20  2:12 am   How did you start getting into making music?

      i don't remember

11.6.20  1:57 am   Do you think potatoes should grow on trees.

      sure

11.6.20  12:55 am   How does one become good at geometry test?

      you're gonna have to understand shapes

11.5.20  11:14 pm   do you think for something to be defined as art, it has to be created by humans?

      i doubt it

11.5.20  10:01 pm   Do you have any plans for more music?

      (calm and collected voice) oh hell yeah

11.5.20  9:41 pm   What's your favorite superlative

      pretty good

11.5.20  9:31 pm    If a coconut has hair and milk is it considered a mammel

      no

11.5.20  9:15 pm   estimated date when will the new song releases?

      i could tell you what i think, but there is a risk i might be wrong, and be chastised for it. and if there's one thing i know about 2020 it's that i'm sick of being chastised

11.5.20  9:14 pm   What ya working on?

      it's one of those songs where it has a music video also, to go along with the song. released as a video, and also as just the song so you can listen to it on-the-go if you prefer

11.5.20  9:02 pm   what has been your biggest inspiration for your videos

      time/space

11.5.20  8:56 pm   Are you god?

      i thought you were

11.5.20  7:59 pm   Are we moving around the universe, or is the universe moving around us?

      it might be impossible to tell

11.5.20  7:30 pm   where did you get the idea of making "at the airport terminal", is it because you like airport terminals?

      i was going to say no but now that i think about it yes

11.5.20  7:27 pm   What's the importance of the pre-chorus?

      to make the song good. i should clarify, it doesn't count if it makes the song worse

11.5.20  7:26 pm   Do I need 3d glasses to see new video

      no, but there might be a version for that

11.5.20  7:23 pm   what is life

      it's you

      no

      make a list of all the things you wish to do when you are un sick
